translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Judging by your faces, looks like you made it in time."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: W-well, congrats to both of you..."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Heh heh heh, this much is a piece of cake!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぶふっ！　マジすか！？」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Since we'll be fighting continuously this time,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "As expected of the prince from the richest country in the world,
